{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-065-066-not-a-baby",
    "title": "Lesson 65: Not a baby",
    "audioFilename": "065&066－Not a Baby.mp3",
    "duration": 95.373,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.5,
      "end": 4.68,
      "text": "Lesson 65–Not a Baby.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第65课——不是小孩子了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 6.5,
      "end": 10.28,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 11.74,
      "end": 15.16,
      "text": "Does Jill take the key to the front door?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉尔带走前门钥匙了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 17.66,
      "end": 21.46,
      "text": "What are you going to do this evening, Jill?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉尔，你今晚打算做什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 22.44,
      "end": 25.8,
      "text": "I'm going to meet some friends, Dad.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我打算去见几个朋友，爸爸。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 26.8,
      "end": 29.26,
      "text": "You mustn't come home late.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你不许回家太晚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 30.2,
      "end": 33.8,
      "text": "You must be home at half past ten.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你必须十点半到家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 34.94,
      "end": 38.2,
      "text": "I can't get home so early, Dad.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我没法那么早回家，爸爸。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 39.42,
      "end": 46.72,
      "text": "Can I have the key to the front door, No, you can't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我能带前门钥匙吗？不，你不能。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 47.72,
      "end": 50.98,
      "text": "Jill's eighteen years old, Tom.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "吉尔已经十八岁了，汤姆。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 51.96,
      "end": 53.78,
      "text": "She's not a baby.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她不是小孩子了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 54.78,
      "end": 56.06,
      "text": "Give her the key.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "把钥匙给她吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 57.02,
      "end": 59.78,
      "text": "She always comes home early.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她一向回家很早。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 61.16,
      "end": 62.8,
      "text": "Oh, all right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "哦，那好吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 64.24,
      "end": 65.56,
      "text": "Here you are.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "给你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 66.3,
      "end": 70.7,
      "text": "But you mustn't come home after a quarter past eleven.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "但你不能晚于十一点一刻回家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 71.56,
      "end": 72.56,
      "text": "Do you hear?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听见了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 73.46,
      "end": 74.56,
      "text": "Yes, Dad.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听见了，爸爸。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 75.82,
      "end": 76.8,
      "text": "Thanks, Mom.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "谢谢，妈妈。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 77.88,
      "end": 79.04,
      "text": "That's all right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不用谢。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 79.84,
      "end": 80.4,
      "text": "Goodbye.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "再见。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 81.78,
      "end": 82.86,
      "text": "Enjoy yourself.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "玩得开心。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 84.38,
      "end": 87.42,
      "text": "We always enjoy ourselves, Mom.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们总会玩得很开心，妈妈。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 88.36,
      "end": 89,
      "text": "Bye-bye.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "再见。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
